				<p>To have less fat and crisper oven bacon try Turkey Bacon.  It&#8217;s better for you to. </p>
<p>It comes in wider pieces that don&#8217;t shrink up as much and you would use less for each of the cup/bowls.  </p>
<p>It will stay crispy even if you need to put it into the frig. for a few days.  Pork bacon doesn&#8217;t do that.</p>
 
