		<li class="comment " id="comment-362646">
			<p class="comment_meta">
				<span class="comment_num"><a href="#comment-362646" title="Permalink to this comment">416</a></span>
				<strong>Katie Vonderhaar </strong>
				<span class="comment_time">// Dec 23, 2009 at 7:47 am</span>
			</p>
			<div class="entry">
				<p>Mayo Dressing:<br />
1 egg<br />
1.5 tbs lemon juice<br />
1/4 tsp sea salt<br />
Pinch of pepper<br />
1 tsp dijon mustard<br />
1/2 cup oil<br />
Fresh basil, shredded</p>
<p>Whisk the egg yolks, lemon juice, salt and pepper.  Whisk in the oil a tbs at a time.  (The more you whisk, the thicker it will get).  Add in the mustard and basil.</p>
 
							</div>
		</li>
		
			
		<li class="comment trackback" id="comment-362648">
